    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/7e8de01abf4bc3ba558c2406f1d9865e.avif?t=1768471212\" width=612 height=198 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏简介：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >『来参加我的派对！』是一部温暖治愈的黑色喜剧视觉小说，故事发生在1999年的韩国小学。游戏讲述了10岁小女孩智敏渴望举办人生第一次生日派对的故事。通过丰富的剧情分支和结局，带你重返纯真年代，唤醒尘封已久的童年回忆。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/bd09554c45ec6b9208e57658cf023014.poster.avif?t=1768471212\" width=626 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/bd09554c45ec6b9208e57658cf023014.webm?t=1768471212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/bd09554c45ec6b9208e57658cf023014.mp4?t=1768471212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事背景：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;只要你能当上班长，就给你办生日派对。&quot;这个意外的机会让智敏看到了希望。一直生活在优等生姐姐和讨喜的弟弟阴影下的她，终于等到了妈妈这个出人意料的提议——这会是她人生第一次当主角的机会吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/b19c0741892ae211a18167935d575e54.poster.avif?t=1768471212\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/b19c0741892ae211a18167935d575e54.webm?t=1768471212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/b19c0741892ae211a18167935d575e54.mp4?t=1768471212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >韩国90年代校园风：完美还原90年代韩国小学的独特氛围</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >丰富剧情分支：12个不同结局等你探索——智敏能交到真心朋友吗？能当选班长吗？能办成梦想中的派对吗？一切都取决于你的选择</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特叙事风格：黑色幽默中带着温暖，完美诠释了童年时期的欢乐与成长烦恼</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >个性鲜明的角色：每个配角都有自己的故事，等待你去发掘他们隐藏的秘密</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/4cf471eecfafb21e164fc2f9335356c3.poster.avif?t=1768471212\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/4cf471eecfafb21e164fc2f9335356c3.webm?t=1768471212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/4cf471eecfafb21e164fc2f9335356c3.mp4?t=1768471212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏目标：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在智敏追寻完美生日派对的旅程中，你将帮助她处理友情、学校纷争和家庭关系。每个选择都会让故事走向不同的结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >让我们一起回到1999年，回到最好的朋友就是整个世界的美好时光。在『来参加我的派对！』中，帮助智敏实现她的生日愿望吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/5ace393653b12d29908e3466d996e3da.poster.avif?t=1768471212\" width=720 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/5ace393653b12d29908e3466d996e3da.webm?t=1768471212\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3003760/extras/5ace393653b12d29908e3466d996e3da.mp4?t=1768471212\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
